Welcome to the Data Manager Portal

Welcome to the Data Manager Portal for the MOLGENIS catalogue.

If this is your first time visiting this page, welcome!

This is where data managers add metadata for their data collections that are part of the MOLGENIS catalogue. You can upload codebooks, descriptive metadata, variable mappings and harmonisations. To find out how this is done, please visit our documentation page. If you are a data manager of a data collection and are interested in joining the catalogue, please let us know by emailing us at support@molgenis.org. This will make your collection more findable for users looking for data to work with and increase visibility.

If you have been here before, hello again!
